Content: [dscrdeql] <✌Jellysmash✌> @AndronicusBass-Founder actually the new welfare card was developed by the company I work for, for the government. I helped develop it. At work we have a couple of months of work to make changes to the system before the government will roll it out.  I won't be working on it this time, but I'm keen to hear about the changes and how well the system gets accepted in Bundaberg.
